				</crossref>
				loathe my life;
				<end-line class="br">
				</end-line>
				<begin-line
					>
				</begin-line>
				I will give free utterance to my 
				<crossref let="v" cid="c18010001.2">
				</crossref>
				complaint;
				<end-line class="br">
				</end-line>
				<begin-line class="indent">
				</begin-line>
				I will speak in 
				<crossref let="w" cid="c18010001.3">
